subject: Tennis
Australian Open (Tennis)
lead_paragraph: Angelique Kerber, inspired by Steffi Graf, her idol and fellow German, will play in the Australian Open final against Serena Williams, who can tie Graf’s Open-era record of 22 major singles titles.
